abstract_ssm: John T. Gilroy was a member and officer of the County Fermanagh Social and Benevolent Association of New York, and of Ancient Order of Hibernians Division 3 (William B. Burke), New York County. This collection consists of personal material, as well as materials concerning Gilroy's membership in various social and fraternal organizations, including the Ancient Order of Hibernians, New York County, Division 3 and the County Fermanagh Social & Benevolent Association of New York. Materials include artifacts, photographs, correspondence, meeting minutes, event programs, newspaper clippings, and various organizational records.
